      <title>欧洲央行行长卡济米尔表示 12 月利率会议前景广阔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/ecb-s-kazimir-says-december-s-rate-meeting-is-wide-open</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员彼得·卡西米尔 (Peter Kazimir) 表示，欧洲央行在 2024 年最后一次会议上仍将保持灵活性，他表示，通货紧缩处于“稳固基础”上，并且可能进一步削减借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/ecb-s-kazimir-says-december-s-rate-meeting-is-wide-open</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选对市场意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/what-the-us-election-between-harris-and-trump-means-for-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年最重要的事件之一——11 月 5 日的美国总统大选——还有几天就要举行了。对于华尔街来说，民主党候选人副总统卡马拉·哈里斯与共和党前总统、候选人唐纳德·特朗普之间的竞争增加了一层波动性，而此时利率、劳动力市场的不确定性以及欧洲和中东的冲突已经考验着投资者的神经。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/what-the-us-election-between-harris-and-trump-means-for-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:08:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛称投资者希望更多地涉足私人信贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/investors-want-more-exposure-to-private-credit-goldman-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 的一项私人市场调查显示，许多投资者认为他们在私人信贷方面的投资不足，并正在寻找更多方式来分一杯羹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/investors-want-more-exposure-to-private-credit-goldman-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金押注绿色转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-21/hedge-funds-bet-against-green-transition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博新闻社对约 500 家对冲基金向 Hazeltree 自愿披露的头寸进行了分析，结果显示，平均而言，净做空电池、太阳能、电动汽车和氢能的对冲基金数量多于做多这些行业的基金数量；净做多化石燃料的基金数量多于做空石油、天然气和煤炭的基金数量。彭博社的 Tasneem Brogger 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-21/hedge-funds-bet-against-green-transition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 10:49:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通数据显示，随着美国大选临近，美元需求激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/jpmorgan-figures-show-surging-dollar-demand-as-us-election-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co) 策略师援引其专有指标表示，由于投资者押注美国大选前夕美元将上涨，上周美元需求激增，而且这种购买势头可能会持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/jpmorgan-figures-show-surging-dollar-demand-as-us-election-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 10:46:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛策略师称标普 500 指数十年大涨已结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/s-p-500-s-decade-of-big-gains-is-over-goldman-strategists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团策略师表示，由于投资者转向债券等其他资产以获得更好的回报，美国股市不太可能维持过去十年的高于平均水平的表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/s-p-500-s-decade-of-big-gains-is-over-goldman-strategists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 08:19:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于利润率下降，Kotak 股价创 6 月以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/kotak-shares-slide-the-most-since-april-as-margins-squeezed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于监管机构禁止客户注册其在线平台和信用卡，科塔克马辛德拉银行有限公司 (Kotak Mahindra Bank Ltd.) 的利润率受到挤压，该公司股价遭遇了 6 月初以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/kotak-shares-slide-the-most-since-april-as-margins-squeezed</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 07:39:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班的经济增长令投资者担心动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/orban-s-push-for-growth-leaves-hungary-investors-fearing-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利政府正在采取惯用的干预经济策略，这让投资者担心该国资产在 2026 年大选前夕将继续表现不佳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/orban-s-push-for-growth-leaves-hungary-investors-fearing-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 06:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国银行降息助力房地产市场 金属价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/metals-rise-after-chinese-banks-cut-rates-to-aid-property-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国各银行下调基准贷款利率之后，铜和锌等工业金属价格上涨，这是北京方面为确保国家经济实现今年的增长目标而采取的举措之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/metals-rise-after-chinese-banks-cut-rates-to-aid-property-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 03:33:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着焦点转向收益，美国期货小幅走低：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/asian-stocks-to-rise-after-wall-street-win-streak-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股指期货下跌，投资者期待本周各大公司公布财报，以进一步了解经济实力。由于中东局势紧张，油价上涨，金价创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/asian-stocks-to-rise-after-wall-street-win-streak-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 22:39:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
